{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act16d5_level_act16d5_01_beg","storyGroup":"act16d5","storySort":2,"storyDependence":"act16d5_level_act16d5_st01","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"WR-1","storyName":"初醒","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"听罢了说书人的故事，炎熔一行已然身处一座奇异小镇。种种古怪却让他们意识到，自己也许已经身陷困境。\n","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act16d5/level_act16d5_01_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act16d5_01","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":0,"next":2,"characters":["村民","说书人","孩子","炎熔","克洛丝","乌有"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"StopSound","channel":"bgs","id":5},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_black","screenadapt":"coverall","id":6},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"PlayMusic","key":"$midautumn","volume":"0.4","id":8,"musicid":0},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$gavel2","volume":"1","id":9},{"type":"dialog","id":10},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":11},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"书接上回，说那跛脚书生败兴而归，自此之后，郁郁不得志。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":12},{"type":"Subtitle","id":13},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":14},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_138#4","fadetime":"1","id":15},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":16},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":17},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"哪件事？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":18},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"自然是画。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":19},{"type":"subtitle","id":20},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"什么画？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":21},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"是那书生痛失故友，心如死灰，一蹶不振十数载后，再一次地灵犀一动——他打定心思，殚心竭虑，发誓要完成那幅毕生力作。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":22},{"type":"subtitle","id":23},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"要画什么？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":24},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"要画未见之物。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":25},{"type":"subtitle","id":26},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"要如何画？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":27},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"得作未想之想。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":28},{"type":"subtitle","id":29},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":30},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"诶，话说到这儿，就有点儿意思了。各位都知道，人所想象之极限，一定是所见所知的经验。要靠想象勾勒出未曾知晓的事物，骗别人简单，骗自己，难如登天。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":31},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"毕竟这天底下，哪有能想出自己没见过的东西的能人呢？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":32},{"type":"subtitle","id":33},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":34},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"那书生对着白纸苦思十来天，瘦了足足三十多斤。本就跛脚，形貌越发恐怖。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":35},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$blizzard","channel":"bgs","volume":"1","loop":"true","block":"false","id":36},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"时入深冬，书生家早已断粮。邻里害怕他那副模样，皆不敢近。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":37},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"直到某天，跛脚书生几度朦胧醒来，四肢无力，却头脑清明。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":38},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_white","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"3","id":39},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"他深知自己大限将至。环顾四周，家徒四壁，恍惚间，只感觉四下无物，真真正正变成了孑然一身。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":40},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":41},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"书生逐渐看不见眼前被大雪打湿又冻上的地面，再听不见门窗漏出的风雪动静。睁眼眨眼，落入混沌，感到墙壁正在远游离去，书案消散，笔墨纸砚皆如过眼云烟。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":42},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"某个时刻，他忽然得知了窗外鹅毛大雪的具体数目，得知了月光的角度与云层的真理。他伸手摸索夜幕，又不小心摔倒在地，地面却不再是双脚的阻碍，他坠向地底，而又飞向深空。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":43},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"他睁眼却不能看，凝神却不能听，周遭黑暗一片——他却反而忽地狂喜起来，好像只有在这绝无外物干扰的境地，他才能寻到真正的创作，而非对其他已有事物的临摹与亵渎。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":44},{"type":"soundvolume","channel":"bgs","volume":"0","fadetime":"5","id":45},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"他继续等，等到寂灭一片，连自己干枯的肉身也感受不到，他才开始思考——只有在这万事万物都不复存在，唯有他的意识独自清明时，他短暂地成为了他精神的主宰。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":46},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_light","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":47},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"他的想象再也不受拘束，创造着存在也不存在的事物——在他思维的疆土上，各种怪诞平地而起，盖过了现实。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":48},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"那天深夜，隔壁起夜的老夫子，看见跛脚书生的茅屋里流光溢彩，光怪陆离，发出各种平生未闻的声响，难以名状。老夫子起胆，就隔着墙偷瞄了一眼。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":49},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"只那一眼，便再不敢深究。他匆匆忙忙回到屋里，久久不得入眠。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":50},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"隔天，邻里纷纷来到茅屋前，夺门而入，发现了书生的遗体，再无别物。大家都以为他是冻死的，村长上前一看，书生面前摊着一张白纸，落满了霜，啥也没画。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":51},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"事后，人们便感慨书生走不出过往，痴死在画卷前。也有说是书生早就染了怪病，控制不住自己的法术，才整出这些怪事。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":52},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"唯一窥见真相的老夫子，却从不对别人说起这件事。只是在他临终前，他对自己的儿子说，那被人唾弃，连名字都被忘记的跛脚书生，是真正的千古大家。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":53},{"type":"soundvolume","channel":"bgs","volume":"1","fadetime":"4","id":54},{"type":"subtitle","id":55},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":56},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":57},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":58},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_landscape","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":59},{"type":"StopSound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"1","id":60},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":61},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":62},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":63},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":64},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":65},{"type":"Character","id":66},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":67},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_140#2","id":68},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"村民","text":"为啥子？","id":69,"figure":"avg_npc_140#2"},{"type":"dialog","id":70},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":71},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"$path_loop","volume":"0.4","id":72,"musicid":1},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_140#2","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"2","id":73},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"因为那个跛脚书生在那晚切实完成了诺言，切实画出了“世间从未有过之物”。","id":74,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_140#2","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"1","id":75},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"村民","text":"咋感觉和书上写的内容不大一样？","id":76,"figure":"avg_npc_140#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_140#2","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"2","id":77},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"老夫子来不及说出为什么，或者压根就说不出为什么就咽了气。","id":78,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"于是坊间流传的说辞，就只有跛脚书生从春风得意到失魂落魄的这么一段。","id":79,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"至于真相如何，恐怕无人知道了。","id":80,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_140#2","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"1","id":81},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"村民","text":"可是画没见过的东西，那有啥难的嘛，我回去乱涂一幅，你们不也没见过。","id":82,"figure":"avg_npc_140#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_140#2","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"2","id":83},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"欸，话不能这么说。你从没见过大湖，但见过雨后积水，我便告诉你，湖是很多的积水。说到底，你还是见过的。","id":84,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"这跛脚书生，厉害就厉害在这儿了。","id":85,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_140#2","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"1","id":86},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"村民","text":"那照你这么说，他到底画了啥？","id":87,"figure":"avg_npc_140#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_140#2","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"2","id":88},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"谁知道呢。","id":89,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_140#2","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"1","id":90},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"村民","text":"嗨，能不能别老讲这么复杂的，咱不爱听啊，啥时候讲讲其他的？","id":91,"figure":"avg_npc_140#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_138#4","name2":"avg_npc_142#2","focus":"2","id":92},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"孩子","text":"我要听上次那“形单影只向天去，雌雄双剑分天下”的大结局！","id":93,"figure":"avg_npc_142#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_138#4","name2":"avg_npc_142#2","focus":"1","id":94},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"会讲的，都会讲的。天下讲不完的事，我用寥寥百年的阳寿去讲，要是还奢求面面俱到，就有点贪得无厌了。","id":95,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"既然你们想听，那下一回，咱们就讲点别的。","id":96,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_138#4","name2":"avg_npc_142#2","focus":"2","id":97},{"type":"jump","name":"right","xpos":"0","power":"40","times":"3","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":98},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"孩子","text":"好诶！","id":99,"figure":"avg_npc_142#2"},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":100},{"type":"dialog","id":101},{"type":"Character","id":102},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":103},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_138#4","id":104},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"老规矩，我这张嘴，不值钱。但是诸位的茶钱，得看着给。","id":105,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"今儿似乎有几位新面孔，不知三位客人对我这些奇闻怪谈，可还满意？","id":106,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"dialog","id":107},{"type":"Character","id":108},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":109},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_144#5","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":110},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":111},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_144#5","focus":"1","id":112},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......","id":113,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_144#5","focus":"2","id":114},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"......","id":115,"figure":"avg_npc_144#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","id":116},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"......这是真事儿？","id":117,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"2","id":118},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"若是说有个书生染了矿石病，遂愿之前便郁郁而终，我倒确信是件真事。","id":119,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"添油加醋，方有滋味啊。","id":120,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"1","id":121},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"在理！","id":122,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"2","id":123},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"多谢。","id":124,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_138#4","id":125},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"只不过，我也不知道这些奇闻野史，到底有几分是真的......只是有这方面的兴趣，仅此而已。","id":126,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"话说回来，我虽然不是什么正儿八经的说书人，也在镇上以此打发了许久光阴，不过愿意来听我胡说八道的，其实就那么几位。","id":127,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"这看着三位面生，不知？","id":128,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"dialog","id":129},{"type":"Character","id":130},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","id":131},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":132},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":133},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"30","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":134},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"咳——（使眼色）","id":135,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"-30","fadetime":"0.5","block":"false","id":136},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#4","focus":"2","id":137},{"type":"jump","name":"right","power":"20","fadetime":"0.5","block":"false","id":138},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"啊——是了是了，我这两位朋友，远道而来，要找个人。","id":139,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#4"},{"type":"dialog","id":140},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":141},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"1","id":142},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"不过这二位在咱们大炎这儿人生地不熟的，所以我就略帮小忙，代为引路，不知先生怎么称呼？","id":143,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"2","id":144},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"我离家多年，早就弃了旧名不用。早年舞文弄墨，自号“煮伞居士”，虽有些恬不知耻，但也沿用至今。","id":145,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"1","id":146},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"好意境！好意境啊！这不巧了，小弟也是被迫无奈，背井离乡，如今也只好借“乌有”二字暂代姓名，不如你就喊我乌老弟呗？","id":147,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"1","id":148},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"（我就说他这名字是编的吧——！？）","id":149,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"2","id":150},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"（嘘......）","id":151,"figure":"avg_npc_144#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"1","id":152},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"（克洛丝？你发现什么了？）","id":153,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"2","id":154},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"（嗯？啊，没有啦，我只是觉得看他每次都要生编硬套很好玩嘛。）","id":155,"figure":"avg_npc_144#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"1","id":156},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"（......）","id":157,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"2","id":158},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"原来同是天涯沦落人，那不知道三位要找的人，是谁？","id":159,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"1","id":160},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"嗨，俗话说得好，相逢即是缘，真是巧得不能再巧了。我们要找的人，也是个画家。","id":161,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_138#1","focus":"2","id":162},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"......画家？这小镇不大，可从未听说过有什么画家。是个什么样的人？","id":163,"figure":"avg_npc_138#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_138#1","focus":"1","id":164},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"呃......恩人？您给说说？","id":165,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#3"},{"type":"dialog","id":166},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","fadetime":"0.7","id":167},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":168},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"1","id":169},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"是一位女性。呃，头上应该长着奇特的角。还会一些奇特的法术。然后......然后......是个画家。","id":170,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"2","id":171},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"就这样？","id":172,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"1","id":173},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......就这样。","id":174,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"2","id":175},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"你这么一说，就更没印象了。","id":176,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"dialog","id":177},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","fadetime":"0.7","id":178},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":179},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"1","id":180},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"唔，这就奇了怪了......莫非二位恩人要找的人，已经离开了这里？","id":181,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"2","id":182},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"这小镇极少有来客，要是如各位所说，那位奇人当给我们留下印象才是。我可以托人帮你问问。","id":183,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"1","id":184},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"好，好，那就不叨扰先生了，我们这就——","id":185,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0","fadetime":"1","id":186},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"这就......？","id":187,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"2","id":188},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"乌有先生？","id":189,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","id":190},{"type":"dialog","id":191},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":192},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#3","focus":"1","id":193},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"喂，你怎么了？","id":194,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"1","id":195},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#4","focus":"2","id":196},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"啊，嘿嘿，我们......我们是从哪儿进来的？","id":197,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#4","focus":"1","id":198},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"你在说什么，我们不是——","id":199,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_138#4","id":200},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"——沿着这条小道，便可离开园林。","id":201,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"想必几位是跟着人群来这里，迷了路吧？哈哈，我这园子不大不小，实在认不得路，问个佣人便是。","id":202,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"1","id":203},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"嘿......你瞧我这糊涂的，怎么就记不住了呢。","id":204,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"2","id":205},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"若是关于那位画家，找到了什么线索需要帮忙，尽管问我。","id":206,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"说书人","text":"我还有点事情，诸位，不送。","id":207,"figure":"avg_npc_138#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","focus":"1","id":208},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"诶，多谢多谢，不用送，不用送。二位恩人，我们先走吧？","id":209,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"dialog","id":210},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","id":211},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":212},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":213},{"type":"Character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_138#4","fadetime":"1","id":214},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":215},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","id":216},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":217},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"1","id":218},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"等等——","id":219,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5"},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":220},{"type":"Character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","fadetime":"0.7","id":221},{"type":"dialog","id":222},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":223},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","delay":"1","id":224},{"type":"Character","name":"char_empty","name2":"char_empty","fadetime":"1.2","delay":"1","id":225},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":226},{"type":"Dialog","id":227},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":228},{"type":"Character","id":229},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":230},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_town","screenadapt":"coverall","id":231},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":232},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":233},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":234},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","fadetime":"1","id":235},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":236},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"接下来，咱们去哪儿瞧瞧？这茶馆，驿站，园子都去过了，还有啥地儿可能有线索的？","id":237,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":238},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......我们到这里多久了？","id":239,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":240},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"唔，怎么突然问这个？大概......三两天时日？","id":241,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":242},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"你确定？","id":243,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#4","focus":"2","id":244},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"啊哈哈，嗨，多半是昨天晚上没睡好，我有点犯迷糊嘞。","id":245,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#4"},{"type":"dialog","id":246},{"type":"Character","id":247},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":248},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":249},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_144#2","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","focus":"1","id":250},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"小炎熔。","id":251,"figure":"avg_npc_144#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_144#2","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","focus":"2","id":252},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"嗯......我感觉到了......但是很模糊的......好像......","id":253,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_144#2","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","focus":"1","id":254},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"这种时候还是要跟着直觉走。","id":255,"figure":"avg_npc_144#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_144#2","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","focus":"2","id":256},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"直觉告诉我，现在情况很麻烦。","id":257,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_144#2","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","focus":"1","id":258},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"是某种精神层面的源石技艺......？","id":259,"figure":"avg_npc_144#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_144#2","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","focus":"2","id":260},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"嗯......法术的话......","id":261,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":262},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"二位恩人，还嘀咕啥呢？再不走快点，天就要黑啦。","id":263,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":264},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"说什么呢，天色还——","id":265,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","id":266},{"type":"dialog","id":267},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":268},{"type":"Character","id":269},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$calamity_intro","key":"$calamity_loop","volume":"0.4","id":270,"musicid":2},{"type":"Image","image":"avg_ac16_1","fadetime":"0","id":271},{"type":"ImageTween","xScaleFrom":"1.05","yScaleFrom":"1.05","xScaleTo":"0.95","yScaleTo":"0.95","ease":"OutCubic","duration":"15","block":"false","id":272},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":273},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":274},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"——","id":275},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"——天......色？","id":276},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"我们竟然从来没有看过天空......？明明只要一抬头就能发现的......真奇怪。","id":277},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"恩、恩人，这是啥情况？你看那边儿，好像......好像都出月亮了呀！？","id":278},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"可现在不是大白天吗，桥那头怎么都点灯笼了？","id":279},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"看身后......","id":280},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"耶？","id":281},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......另一个方向的天边，那是......是太阳？","id":282},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"啊，是不是从那头到这头走个来回，就相当于\"走过了\"一天一夜？","id":283},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"这还真......新奇。总是听年说大炎地大物博无奇不有......还有这种景观？","id":284},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"唔，等等，我口袋里好像有什么东西......","id":285},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"这是，年给我的护身符......？","id":286},{"type":"dialog","id":287},{"type":"ShowItem","image":"item_act16_1","fadestyle":"horiz_expand_center","fadetime":"0.5","offsetx":"0","width":"200","id":288},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":289},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$tactfulboost","volume":"0.6","id":290},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":291},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":292},{"type":"Image","id":293},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5","id":294},{"type":"hideitem","id":295},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":296},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":297},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":298},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"慢着......慢着！不对，不对！","id":299,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"什么叫“这种景观”啊，我刚才在想什么......！","id":300,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_144#5","id":301},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"啊......","id":302,"figure":"avg_npc_144#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5","id":303},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"乌有！","id":304,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#3","focus":"2","id":305},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"诶——？我在，我在！","id":306,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#3","focus":"1","id":307},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"这里到底是不是泥翁镇！？","id":308,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#3","focus":"2","id":309},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"这......这还用说......呃......","id":310,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"这，这仔细看看似乎是有点不对，可这附近也没有别的镇子了呀！","id":311,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","id":312},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......还是不对，不对。","id":313,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","focus":"2","id":314},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"克洛丝，我们从罗德岛出发，先抵达了勾吴城，补给之后，翌日上午出城。","id":315,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","focus":"1","id":316},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"然后我们在前往灰齐山的荒原上看见了一辆撞毁的车——","id":317,"figure":"avg_npc_144#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"1","id":318},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"——然后二位恩人从那些畜生手里救下了我？","id":319,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"2","id":320},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"只是把它们带到了适合筑巢的新窝而已啦。它们也挺不容易的。","id":321,"figure":"avg_npc_144#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","id":322},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"然后呢？","id":323,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","id":324},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"然后我们......？","id":325,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","id":326},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"嗯嗯，然后我们直接登上了灰齐山，找到了一间破茅屋。","id":327,"figure":"avg_npc_144#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","id":328},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"我推开了那儿的......","id":329,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......门？","id":330,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4"},{"type":"dialog","id":331},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":332},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":333},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$bigbell","channel":"bgs","volume":"1","loop":"true","id":334},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":335},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"钟声？哪里的钟声？","id":336,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4"},{"type":"dialog","id":337},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":338},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$corrosion_intro","key":"$corrosion_loop","volume":"0.4","id":339,"musicid":3},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_140#1","name2":"avg_npc_140#1","focus":"1","id":340},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"40","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":341},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"村民","text":"敲钟了？敲钟了！喂，快去把家里人都喊起来！动作快！","id":342,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_140#1","name2":"avg_npc_140#1","focus":"2","id":343},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"村民","text":"怎么回事！都这么长时间了！为什么会是今天！","id":344,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"StopSound","channel":"bgs","id":345},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5","name2":"avg_npc_140#1","focus":"1","id":346},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"那个......！请问发生什么了！？","id":347,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5","name2":"avg_npc_140#1","focus":"2","id":348},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"村民","text":"你们，你们是外人？敲钟就说明西边的山里来怪物啦！","id":349,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"村民","text":"那些怪物见不得光，只要跑到有太阳的地方，就安全了！","id":350,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_140#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#3","focus":"2","id":351},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"怪，怪物？什么怪物？","id":352,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_140#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#3","focus":"1","id":353},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"40","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":354},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"村民","text":"哎呀，没空和你瞎唠叨啦！别挡着我，我得把老婆带到这儿来呀！","id":355,"figure":"avg_npc_140#1"},{"type":"exit","name":"left","direction":"right","fadetime":"1.2","block":"false","id":356},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":357},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"50","fadetime":"0.5","block":"false","id":358},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":359},{"type":"Character","id":360},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":361},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"false","block":"false","id":362},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$bigbell","channel":"bgs","volume":"1","loop":"true","id":363},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":364},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.7","delay":"0.4","id":365},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.4","delay":"0.7","id":366},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.3","delay":"1.2","id":367},{"type":"StopSound","channel":"bgs","id":368},{"type":"delay","time":"1 ","id":369},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"孩子","text":"妈妈！妈妈！","id":370},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"村民","text":"都在这儿了吗？还少谁！快去找找！","id":371},{"type":"dialog","id":372},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#3","id":373},{"type":"CameraShake","id":374},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"40","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":375},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"恩人，恩人，咱们也赶紧去避难吧！","id":376,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"说是只要跑到有太阳的地方就没事儿了？那咱们赶紧——恩人？","id":377,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#3"},{"type":"dialog","id":378},{"type":"Character","id":379},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":380},{"type":"CameraShake","stop":"true","id":381},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","fadetime":"0.6","id":382},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":383},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"2","id":384},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......克洛丝。","id":385,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_144#2","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","focus":"1","id":386},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"准备好啦。","id":387,"figure":"avg_npc_144#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_144#2","name2":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5","focus":"2","id":388},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"好。","id":389,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5"},{"type":"dialog","id":390},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"1","id":391},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":392},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.7","delay":"0.4","id":393},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$atkboost","volume":"0.6","id":394},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$atkboost","volume":"0.7","delay":"0.3","id":395},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":396},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#3","id":397},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"——恩人！？别闹啦，我们自个儿都是一团浆糊，还是先躲躲再说吧！","id":398,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"诶！诶诶！这怎么就冲过去了！唉！我的好恩人呐，你们——等我，等我一下啊！","id":399,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#3"},{"type":"dialog","id":400},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"1.5","id":401},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":402},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":403},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":404},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":405},{"type":"Dialog","id":406},{"type":"Character","id":407},{"type":"Image","id":408}],"characters":["村民","说书人","孩子","炎熔","克洛丝","乌有"]}